- Pig version 0.9.1 with Hadoop 0.20.205 to consider AWS
- download http://archive.apache.org/dist/pig/pig-0.9.1/pig-0.9.1.tar.gz

export PIG_HOME=/root/pig-0.9.1
export PATH=$PIG_HOME/bin/:$PATH
export PIG_CLASSPATH=/root/hadoop-0.20.205.0/conf

or 

export HADOOP_HOME=/root/hadoop-0.20.205.0/ (this is a must)
pig -x mapreduce /work/samples/Pig/WordCount.pig 

